[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 10     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m <!-- What is the problem? What change do you believe will improve the target agent? Why? -->
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      10[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The system prompt provides incorrect API discovery instructions (`search_apis` doesn't exist), no guidance on authentication token passing, and insufficient step budget (MAX_STEPS=10). Rewriting the system prompt with correct API patterns (`show_api_descriptions`, `show_api_doc`), explicit auth token instructions, pagination guidance, and increasing MAX_STEPS to 25 will fix the fundamental inability of the agent to discover APIs and authenticate — enabling it to complete tasks that were previously impossible.
