[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 26    [0m:[38;5;9m[49m - Agent doesn't pass access_token to authenticated API calls after login
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 27    [0m:[38;5;9m[49m - Agent guesses API names instead of discovering them via docs
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 28    [0m:[38;5;9m[49m - MAX_STEPS=10 is too low for complex multi-app tasks when steps are wasted on errors
